---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /trending/
title: Hall of Shame
description: The most-blamed AI slop on AISlopWatch, ranked live by reader blames and views.
robots: noindex, follow
---
<a class="back mono" href="{{ '/' | url }}">← all posts</a>

<h1 class="tagpage-title">Hall of <span class="tag">Shame</span></h1>

<p class="intro prose">
  The most-blamed sightings, ranked live by your blames and views. Counts are
  <em>aggregate and cookieless</em> — we tally the slop, not the visitor.
</p>

{% set board = collections.posts | rankByEngagement(engagement) %}
{%- if board.length %}
<div class="board-slab mono">MOST BLAMED <span>// updated live · cookieless</span></div>
<ol class="board" data-board>
  {%- for row in board %}
  <li class="board-row" data-slug="{{ row.post.fileSlug }}">
    <a class="board-link" href="{{ row.post.url | url }}">
      <span class="board-rank mono">{{ loop.index | pad }}</span>
      <span class="board-body">
        <span class="board-title">{{ row.post.data.title }}</span>
        <span class="board-stats mono">
          <span class="board-stat board-score">🔨 <span class="live-votes">{{ row.up }}</span> blames</span>
          <span class="board-stat">👁 <span class="live-views">0</span> views</span>
        </span>
      </span>
      <span class="board-arrow mono" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </li>
  {%- endfor %}
</ol>
{%- else %}
<p class="prose">No sightings logged yet. Bring receipts.</p>
{%- endif %}
